AI Description: FoldSeek is a Python package for predicting RNA secondary structures using deep learning models. It utilizes Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) to learn the complex patterns in RNA sequences and predict the secondary structures.
Core Features: Prediction Of RNA Secondary Structures, Utilizes Deep Learning Models, Specifically Cnns, Python-Based Package, Allows For Training Custom Models
General Tags: RNA Secondary Structure Prediction, Deep Learning Models, Python Package
